{"tid":1202871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政治冷感？放棄香港？","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:48:10.000Z","uid":221616,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd56dcfce84ac352beca969d98c2116b4261a96","tid":1202871,"uid":221616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"好想講<br />\n忍咗好耐<br />\n身邊啲朋友成日喺度屌啲人政治冷感<br />\n喺ig fb 睇到掛住喺吃喝玩樂 <br />\n仲好開心咁<br />\n話自己已經unfriend晒依啲人 覺得呢啲人冷血<br />\n死到臨頭 仲唔知死字係點寫<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n唔同人對呢件事都有唔同睇法<br />\n 冇可能要全香港嘅人上街 反對政府濕鳩送終法<br />\n人哋唔表態有佢嘅原因 <br />\n或者選擇其他方式去幫助<br />\n唔係一定下下都要放喺IG表示自己有去 喺現場抗爭 自己先係愛香港嘅行為？<br />\n而人哋係IG 一個po都冇表示 淨po飲飲食食就話人哋冷血？ 就要unfriend人？<br />\n唔諗下人地可能喺背後做幾多嘢而冇計較？<br />\n最後一句<br />\n公道至在人心<br />\n呢條法例擺明想香港慢慢失去自由 <br />\n但大家嘅表達方式即使唔同<br />\n都唔好因為咁而起衝突<br />\n唔值得."},{"pid":"8482ab99f6eef3379cc3d244ba8fc568394b7b7e","tid":1202871,"uid":251510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china?recruiter=554231063&amp;recruited_by_id=92a49e10-2e1d-11e6-bc11-b193dd1d0f73&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_term=address_book&amp;share_bandit_exp=message-15727601-en-GB&amp;share_bandit_var=v0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china%3Frecruiter%3D554231063%26recruited_by_id%3D92a49e10-2e1d-11e6-bc11-b193dd1d0f73%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dpsf_combo_share_message%26utm_term%3Daddress_book%26share_bandit_exp%3Dmessage-15727601-en-GB%26share_ba